text: Tyreek Hill (born March 1, 1994) is an American Football Wide Receiver for the Miami Dolphins. Originally drafted by the Kansas City Chiefs in 2016, Hill has had a successful career, with one Super Bowl win and being a 4-time All-Pro. One of the fastest players in the NFL, he has reached a top speed of over 20 mph (32 km/hr) in a game. == Notes == Category:Miami Dolphins players
title: Tyreek Hill
